name: Precise Rocket
description:
Play as a rocket Captain, who is lost in unknown planet. fly through and dodge obstacles to find your way and save your crew! But be careful... There are strange things happening there. 

Space - Thrust; A/D - Rotate. 

New C# Developer here. Just started course and made this project. I'm going to still update it tho ;D (I'm not satisfied yet) Any suggestions what to add/change? P.S. It's just a prototype not finished or developing project
